## reckonry importers
$ reckonry importers
RECKONRY
Reviewable digital asset ledger infrastructure.

Alpha source importers
binance | Exchange | Binance CSV Importer | Version 0.1.0 | Scope alpha demo
  Files: Transaction history CSV, Spot trade history CSV, Convert history CSV, Normalized Binance export CSV
  Schemas: UTC_Time,Account,Operation,Coin,Change,Remark, Date(UTC),Market,Type,Price,Amount,Total,Fee,Fee Coin, Date,From Asset,From Amount,To Asset,To Amount,Fee,Fee Coin, datetime_tz_CET,type,sent_amount,sent_currency,received_amount,received_currency,fee_amount,fee_currency
  Operations: Deposits, Withdrawals, Spot trades, Conversions, Rewards and earn entries, Unknown row preservation
coinbase | Exchange | Coinbase CSV Importer | Version 0.1.0-alpha | Scope alpha demo
  Files: Coinbase transaction CSV export, Normalized Coinbase demo CSV
  Schemas: Timestamp,Transaction Type,Asset,Quantity Transacted,Spot Price Currency,Subtotal,Total (inclusive of fees and/or spread),Fees and/or Spread,Notes, timestamp,type,asset,quantity,native_currency,native_amount,fee_amount,fee_currency,received_asset,received_quantity,notes
  Operations: Buys, Sells, Sends, Receives, Rewards and earn entries, Conversions, Unknown row preservation

